{"tid":1314923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（立場）立法會議員+區議員於源禾路組成人鏈","createTime":"2019-07-14T11:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:33:10.000Z","uid":142903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"96515fd60d49ad41a05773190f77c33025bcfe0e","tid":1314923,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"【沙田遊行】<br />\n沙田區今日舉行反送中遊行，到傍晚多處爆出警民衝突。多位立法會議員及區議員在源禾路築成人鍊，要求與在場指揮官對話。需以輪椅代步的沙田區議員葉榮，亦身處示威現場最前線。<br />\n<br />\n【沙田遊行】攝影師記者採訪時遇襲　無綫新聞：嚴厲譴責暴徒，已報警<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XNedlN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XNedlN&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=ca87f4a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XNedlN</a><br />\n<br />\n【睇片】「光復沙田」被海關辭退後從商　林景楠現身遊行：商人有社會責任，更要發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XTiKDu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XTiKDu&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=9b208b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XTiKDu</a><br />\n<br />\n【直播・不斷更新】逾十萬人沙田區遊行　警方施胡椒噴劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JzFEvH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JzFEvH&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=35f022d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JzFEvH</a><br />\n<br />\n75歲張伯：文革偷渡來港，今天年輕人唔知可以去邊　<br />\n媽媽設涼茶站打氣<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32nv6Hg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32nv6Hg&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=186af7be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32nv6Hg</a><br />\n<br />\n擬修憲刪正體字條文　港大研究生會急撤回　學生赴前主席宿舍抗議<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2SeGf8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SeGf8s&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=f2b107d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2SeGf8s</a><br />\n<br />\n*****************<br />\n另見《立場新聞》<br />\nInstagram:<a hr